channel.title: Funny Mopar Quotes
channel.description:
I thought I'd give this thread a shot. Post some funny mscp quotes that you've seen over the years, months, weeks, or days that you've been around. Try not to post a quote that has been already posted.
[b][u]The rules of this thread are as follows:[/u][/b]
[ul][li]You are to follow all Global Rules of the MoparScape forums.[/li] [li]Try not to repost an already posted quote.[/li] [li]No posting a quote originally said by you.[/li] [li]You may merge both MoparScape and Moparisthebest quotes.[/li] [li]You may post quotes from IRC.[/li][/ul]
Otherwise, have fun!
Here, I'll start: [code] wildskiller - I want people to throw shit at me, literally. I'll be glad to be piled in feces.
Team_Rocket - The majority of people are ignorant sheep
Ruby - At what point in your mind did you begin to think that Web Design/Development would be the correct place to post this? What possible chain of thought went through your mind where you thought the correct board for your server issues would be the website development board over the server help board?
Fat Cookies - Luckily most people who play rsps's have the IQ of a rabbit.
Rodgerwilco - Throw your computer out the window and run into the nearest wall.
eyeownyew - Your grammar hurts my eyes.
asshole_rule - I tried advil once. It was badass.
Ogolemx - I find it too confusing... It took me an hour to find commands.java *(thank you search bar).
Miss Silabsoft - "if you can't beat it, DDOS it" - KO9
The Web Guy - http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,598537.msg4209854.html#msg4209854
Miss Silabsoft - no signature is complete without a 20 year old anime that appeals to little boys by showing muscular sweaty men powering up for an episode and a half. -----asshole_rule - silab, they don't 'power up' they go super sayan, love off.
Team_Rocket - Ur s0 c00l 4 smokin dat Ganja man. i wnt 2 b jst liek u when i turn 13. P.S. cn u teech me 2 b UB3rUB3rL337????? [/code]
